    primary400: '#39A7FF',
    primary600: '#39A7FF',
    primary80: '#39A7FFcc',
    primary50: '#39A7FF80',
    primary30: '#39A7FF4d',

    secondary50: '#FFFFFF80',
    tertiary: '#000000',
    tertiary80: '#000000',
    tertiary70: '#000000',
    tertiary50: '#000000',
    aboutimg1: blueThemeboy,
    aboutimg2: blueThemegirl,
    eduimg: eduBlue,
    expimg: expBlue,
    contactsimg: contactsBlue
}
